[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":516},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200924\u002F2892089216\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200924\u002F2892089216\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200924\u002F2892089216\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200924\u002F2892089216\u002F":493,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200924\u002F2892089216\u002F":502},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F24\u002Flearn-hexo-11-deploy-first-blog\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":474,"date":475,"description":18,"extension":476,"lang":477,"meta":478,"navigation":479,"path":480,"readingMinutes":481,"seo":482,"standalone":483,"stem":484,"tags":485,"tldr":490,"updated":490,"url":491,"__hash__":492},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F11-試著學-Hexo-部署你的第一個部落格.md","(11) 試著學 Hexo - 部署你的第一個部落格","2892089216",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":466},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,29,44,47,54,57,60,63,69,78,81,85,99,108,114,117,161,164,169,172,176,179,195,206,276,291,294,297,312,321,335,342,359,366,372,382,386,392,398,405,410,422,429,444,450,456,462],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來將要來部署你的第一個部落格囉。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"github-pages","GitHub Pages",[16,24,25],{},"接下來這邊開始我們將會使用 GitHub 來當作我們網頁的儲存空間，你可能會想說",[16,27,28],{},"「GitHub？GitHub 不是放原始碼的地方嗎？怎麼可以放 Hexo？」",[16,30,31,32,38,39,43],{},"其實 GitHub 本身有提供一個功能叫做 ",[33,34,22],"a",{"href":35,"rel":36},"https:\u002F\u002Fpages.github.com\u002F",[37],"nofollow","，它可以讓你放置你的靜態專案展示頁面，例如我先前無聊做的 ",[33,40,42],{"href":41},"\u002Fw3cHexSchool-Search\u002F#\u002F","六角全馬鐵人搜尋器","就是放置在 gh-pages 上。",[16,45,46],{},"而這邊你可能會想說 GitHub 接受我們將儲存庫當作部落格來使用？其實是可以的，因為在 GitHub Pages 底下就可以看到這三個類別，其中一個就寫著「Blogging with Jekyll」",[16,48,49],{},[50,51],"img",{"alt":52,"src":53},"Blogging with Jekyll","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002FJavaScript%20%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E8%A7%80%E5%BF%B5\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-09%2018.08.00.png",[16,55,56],{},"因此我們可以把 GitHub Pages 當作部落格的空間免費使用，除此之外 GitHub Pages 還有一些好處也就是免費的 HTTPS，如果你是自己架設空間的話，就會需要生成 SSL 證書相對很麻煩。",[16,58,59],{},"(其實還滿多人用 GitHub Pages 當作部落格空間的。)",[16,61,62],{},"所以說 GitHub Pages 就沒有任何限制嗎？其實還是有的，這邊擷取官方的說明(含破英文翻譯)",[64,65,66],"blockquote",{},[16,67,68],{},"GitHub Pages source repositories have a recommended limit of 1GB. For more information, see \"What is my disk quota?\" - GitHub Pages 儲存庫大小限制在 1 GB\nPublished GitHub Pages sites may be no larger than 1 GB. - 發布的 GitHub Pages 內容不得超過 1 GB\nGitHub Pages sites have a soft bandwidth limit of 100GB per month. - GitHub Pages 站點流量每月是 100 GB\nGitHub Pages sites have a soft limit of 10 builds per hour. - GitHub Pages 每小時可接受的更新是 10 個版本。",[16,70,71,72,77],{},"其他詳細你可以",[33,73,76],{"href":74,"rel":75},"https:\u002F\u002Fdocs.github.com\u002Fen\u002Fgithub\u002Fworking-with-github-pages\u002Fabout-github-pages#guidelines-for-using-github-pages",[37],"參考","官方文件比較快。",[16,79,80],{},"但是基本上普通部落格已經很夠用了。",[12,82,84],{"id":83},"建立-github-pages-儲存庫","建立 GitHub Pages 儲存庫",[16,86,87,88,93,94,98],{},"接下來情景是假設你已經建立 or 持有的 GitHub 帳號的狀況下，所以如果你沒有註冊，那麼就請到",[33,89,92],{"href":90,"rel":91},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fjoin?source=login",[37],"這裡","註冊一個( ",[95,96,97],"del",{},"哎，幫 GitHub 打廣告"," )。",[16,100,101,102,107],{},"首先請先新增一個儲存庫(為了避免 GitHub 介面有更新，所以我提供",[33,103,106],{"href":104,"rel":105},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fnew",[37],"建立連結","。)",[16,109,110],{},[50,111],{"alt":112,"src":113},"建立儲存庫","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002FJavaScript%20%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E8%A7%80%E5%BF%B5\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-09%2018.20.24.png",[16,115,116],{},"接下來欄位可以參考我底下說明",[118,119,120,145,153],"ul",{},[121,122,123,124],"li",{},"Repository name\n",[118,125,126],{},[121,127,128,129,133,134,137,138,141,142,144],{},"欄位請輸入 ",[130,131,132],"code",{},"[你的 GitHub 帳號].github.io","，例如我的 Owner 名稱是 ",[130,135,136],{},"hsiangfeng","，所以就要輸入 ",[130,139,140],{},"hsiangfeng.github.io"," (這邊很重要，如果你輸入錯誤，接下來你就無法透過 ",[130,143,132],{}," 進入你的部落格)",[121,146,147,148],{},"Description\n",[118,149,150],{},[121,151,152],{},"基本上隨便你，反正是選填，我是填寫 Hexo Blog",[121,154,155,156],{},"儲存庫類型，請選擇 Public\n",[118,157,158],{},[121,159,160],{},"你如果選 Private 就無法使用唷。",[16,162,163],{},"這邊我用我的小分身當作示範",[16,165,166],{},[50,167],{"alt":112,"src":168},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-09%2019.35.56.png",[16,170,171],{},"這樣你就建立好囉~",[12,173,175],{"id":174},"替-hexo-安裝部署套件","替 Hexo 安裝部署套件",[16,177,178],{},"接下來我們必須替 Hexo 安裝部署用的套件，因為本身 Hexo 並沒有預載一鍵部署的功能所以必須額外安裝套件",[180,181,186],"pre",{"className":182,"code":183,"language":184,"meta":185,"style":185},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","npm install --save hexo-deployer-git\n","cmd","",[130,187,188],{"__ignoreMap":185},[189,190,193],"span",{"class":191,"line":192},"line",1,[189,194,183],{},[16,196,197,198,201,202,205],{},"安裝完畢之後打開 Hexo 的 ",[130,199,200],{},"hexo\u002F_config.yml","(注意，不是主題的 ",[130,203,204],{},"themes\u002F_config.yml",")，並在結尾處加入以下",[180,207,211],{"className":208,"code":209,"language":210,"meta":185,"style":185},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","deploy:\n  type: git\n  repo: https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsianghexo\u002Fhsianghexo.github.io.git # https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002F[你的 GitHub 帳號]\u002F[你的 GitHub 帳號].github.io.git\n  branch: master # 在這邊我是使用 mster 當作主要分支\n  message: 'ithelpt'\n","yml",[130,212,213,223,236,251,265],{"__ignoreMap":185},[189,214,215,219],{"class":191,"line":192},[189,216,218],{"class":217},"sKpQp","deploy",[189,220,222],{"class":221},"sMAXC",":\n",[189,224,226,229,232],{"class":191,"line":225},2,[189,227,228],{"class":217},"  type",[189,230,231],{"class":221},": ",[189,233,235],{"class":234},"sTRMh","git\n",[189,237,239,242,244,247],{"class":191,"line":238},3,[189,240,241],{"class":217},"  repo",[189,243,231],{"class":221},[189,245,246],{"class":234},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fhsianghexo\u002Fhsianghexo.github.io.git",[189,248,250],{"class":249},"sQrFR"," # https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002F[你的 GitHub 帳號]\u002F[你的 GitHub 帳號].github.io.git\n",[189,252,254,257,259,262],{"class":191,"line":253},4,[189,255,256],{"class":217},"  branch",[189,258,231],{"class":221},[189,260,261],{"class":234},"master",[189,263,264],{"class":249}," # 在這邊我是使用 mster 當作主要分支\n",[189,266,268,271,273],{"class":191,"line":267},5,[189,269,270],{"class":217},"  message",[189,272,231],{"class":221},[189,274,275],{"class":234},"'ithelpt'\n",[16,277,278,279,282,283,286,287,290],{},"欄位基本上你就只需要修改 ",[130,280,281],{},"repo","、",[130,284,285],{},"branch","，而 ",[130,288,289],{},"message"," 你可以自己決定是否輸入或者乾脆忽略。",[12,292,293],{"id":293},"部署部落格",[16,295,296],{},"最後一個步驟就是部署 Hexo 到 GitHub 上，在這邊只需要依序輸入以下指令即可",[180,298,300],{"className":182,"code":299,"language":184,"meta":185,"style":185},"hexo generate\nhexo deploy\n",[130,301,302,307],{"__ignoreMap":185},[189,303,304],{"class":191,"line":192},[189,305,306],{},"hexo generate\n",[189,308,309],{"class":191,"line":225},[189,310,311],{},"hexo deploy\n",[16,313,314,315,317,318],{},"但是！在輸入這些指令之前，請你務必修改 ",[130,316,200],{}," 中大約 16 行左右有一個 ",[130,319,320],{},"url",[180,322,324],{"className":208,"code":323,"language":210,"meta":185,"style":185},"url: http:\u002F\u002Fyoursite.com\n",[130,325,326],{"__ignoreMap":185},[189,327,328,330,332],{"class":191,"line":192},[189,329,320],{"class":217},[189,331,231],{"class":221},[189,333,334],{"class":234},"http:\u002F\u002Fyoursite.com\n",[16,336,337,338,341],{},"請務必將這一段修改成你剛剛建立 GitHub 儲存庫的 Url，否則是有可能發生一些問題的，假使你剛剛建立的儲存庫是 ",[130,339,340],{},"hsianghexo.github.io","，那麼就麻煩請改成以下",[180,343,345],{"className":208,"code":344,"language":210,"meta":185,"style":185},"url: https:\u002F\u002Fhsianghexo.github.io # 請小心後面不要多一個「\u002F」否則會出現問題\n",[130,346,347],{"__ignoreMap":185},[189,348,349,351,353,356],{"class":191,"line":192},[189,350,320],{"class":217},[189,352,231],{"class":221},[189,354,355],{"class":234},"https:\u002F\u002Fhsianghexo.github.io",[189,357,358],{"class":249}," # 請小心後面不要多一個「\u002F」否則會出現問題\n",[16,360,361,362,365],{},"接下來這邊你就可以輸入上面的指令了，可是我知道每次都要打相同這麼長的指令很煩，所以你也可以直接輸入 ",[130,363,364],{},"hexo d -g","，這一段的意思就是我要生成靜態網頁並部署",[16,367,368],{},[50,369],{"alt":370,"src":371},"部署到 GitHub","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-09%2019.53.15.png",[16,373,374,375,378,379,381],{},"當畫面出現 ",[130,376,377],{},"Branch 'master' set up to track remote branch 'master'"," 就代表已經部署完畢，但這時候你若在瀏覽器輸入 ",[130,380,340],{}," 可能會發現 404 的頁面，這是因為我們還沒開啟 GitHub Pages (通常來講會自動開啟，但總是會有意外，所以後面會介紹如何手動開啟)。",[12,383,385],{"id":384},"開啟-github-pages","開啟 GitHub Pages",[16,387,388,389],{},"點一下專案儲存庫上方的 ",[130,390,391],{},"Settings",[16,393,394],{},[50,395],{"alt":396,"src":397},"Setting","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002Fsettings.png",[16,399,400,401,404],{},"然後往下滾或者直接搜尋「GitHub Pages」，並將 ",[130,402,403],{},"Source"," 指向到 master 並按下 Save 即可",[16,406,407],{},[50,408],{"alt":261,"src":409},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-09%2019.58.24.png",[16,411,412,413,421],{},"接下來重新整理畫面確定「GitHub Pages」出現 ",[414,415,416,417],"strong",{},"Your site is published at ",[33,418,419],{"href":419,"rel":420},"https:\u002F\u002Fhsianghexo.github.io\u002F",[37],"，那就代表你的部落格上線囉(如果出現還在準備，就稍微等一下就可以囉)。",[16,423,424,425,428],{},"通常來講 GitHub 會有緩存問題，大約 5 ~ 15 min 不等，若你發現一直持續在 404 那麼就會建議你刪除 ",[130,426,427],{},".deploy_git"," 資料夾(通常是隱藏的)，然後在依序輸入以下指令，基本上問題就解決了，這個問題比較常見於初次部署的時候",[180,430,432],{"className":182,"code":431,"language":184,"meta":185,"style":185},"hexo clean\nhexo d -g\n",[130,433,434,439],{"__ignoreMap":185},[189,435,436],{"class":191,"line":192},[189,437,438],{},"hexo clean\n",[189,440,441],{"class":191,"line":225},[189,442,443],{},"hexo d -g\n",[16,445,446],{},[50,447],{"alt":448,"src":449},"部署成功","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F1596975902983.jpg",[16,451,452,453],{},"這一篇長度稍微有一點長，最主要是這一段在部署上是滿多人踩雷，如果沒有講清楚一點...",[95,454,455],{},"我怕你拿鍵盤打我",[16,457,458],{},[50,459],{"alt":460,"src":461},"圖源：網路","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F1526741686922233o10p1n1.gif",[463,464,465],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}",{"title":185,"searchDepth":225,"depth":225,"links":467},[468,469,470,471,472,473],{"id":14,"depth":225,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":225,"text":22},{"id":83,"depth":225,"text":84},{"id":174,"depth":225,"text":175},{"id":293,"depth":225,"text":293},{"id":384,"depth":225,"text":385},"Hexo","2020-09-24 00:00:01","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fhexo\u002F11-hexo","3",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"試著學 Hexo\u002F11-試著學-Hexo-部署你的第一個部落格",[474,486,487,488,489],"試著學 Hexo","第 12 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽","Git","GitHub",null,"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200924\u002F2892089216\u002F","9SieriFLDD2nzsKOpnwaRI3aBX6sQy1a1AIVZpaea2A",{"newer":494,"older":498},{"url":495,"title":